---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import larryLogo from "../../assets/larrysmshub_logo.png";
---

<Layout title="Larry SMS Hub">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 mt-8">
    <Header />
    <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-2">
      <a href="/projects" class="underline decoration-dashed underline-offset-4">← Back to projects</a>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mb-3">
      <img src={larryLogo.src} alt="Larry SMS Hub logo" class="h-10 md:h-12 object-contain" />
      <span class="absolute top-0 right-0 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border text-[11px] border-emerald-100 text-emerald-700 bg-emerald-50/70">Live</span>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Larry SMS Hub</h1>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5 md:gap-2 text-[11px] mb-2">
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Branded Sender ID</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Scheduling & Automation</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Groups & Segments</span>
      <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70">Delivery Reports</span>
    </div>

    <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4 mb-3 md:w-4/5">
      <div class="text-sm text-gray-800">
        <div class="font-semibold mb-1">In one line</div>
        Set it once, grow on time. Larry SMS Hub sends your reminders, promos, and alerts—automatically, with your business name.
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-gray-700 md:w-3/4" style="line-height: 2">
      Built for Ghana’s schools, churches, hospitals, and growing businesses. Larry SMS Hub takes the manual hustle out of messaging so you save time, stay consistent, and deepen trust.
    </p>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Who it’s for</h3>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-[12px]">
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Shops & SMEs</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Schools</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Churches</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">Clinics & Hospitals</span>
          <span class="px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full border border-zinc-200 bg-white/80">NGOs</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What you can do (quick list)</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-2 md:gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1.5">
            <li>Branded Sender ID (e.g., YOURSHOP) — builds trust instantly</li>
            <li>One‑time blasts and recurring schedules</li>
            <li>Templates for promos, fee reminders, service alerts</li>
            <li>Groups & segments (Parents, VIP customers, Ward A)</li>
          </ul>
          <ul class="list-disc ms-5 space-y-1.5">
            <li>Delivery reports and basic analytics</li>
            <li>Import contacts (CSV) and simple list management</li>
            <li>Permissions for staff (who can send what)</li>
            <li>Mobile Money / Card payments</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How it works</h3>
        <ol class="ms-5 list-decimal text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1.5">
          <li>Create groups (Parents 2025, VIP, Department A)</li>
          <li>Write your message or pick a template</li>
          <li>Choose Sender ID and schedule (now, later, recurring)</li>
          <li>We send on time; you track delivery reports</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Pricing</h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-2 md:gap-3 text-sm text-gray-700">
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">Small Pot</div>
            <div class="text-[12px] text-gray-500">For micro teams</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Low monthly fee</li>
              <li>Included SMS bundle</li>
              <li>Scheduling & templates</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">Market Leader</div>
            <div class="text-[12px] text-gray-500">For growing orgs</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Bigger SMS bundle</li>
              <li>Recurring schedules</li>
              <li>Basic analytics</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 bg-white/70 p-3">
            <div class="font-semibold">Gold Coast</div>
            <div class="text-[12px] text-gray-500">For high volume</div>
            <ul class="list-disc ms-5 mt-1 space-y-1.5">
              <li>Very high SMS volume</li>
              <li>Priority support</li>
              <li>Team permissions</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2 text-[12px] text-gray-600">Final pricing depends on SMS volume and Sender ID setup. Let’s match a plan to your needs.</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Trust & compliance</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc ms-5 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-1.5">
          <li>NCA‑aligned Sender ID process</li>
          <li>Local telco routes for high delivery performance</li>
          <li>Opt‑out support and contact hygiene</li>
          <li>Data handled with care and minimal retention</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-4">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-2xl p-3 md:p-4">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">FAQ</h3>
        <div class="text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2.5">
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Can I send with my business name?</div>
            <p>Yes. We set up a branded Sender ID (subject to telco/NCA rules) so your messages come from your name, not a random number.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Can I automate reminders?</div>
            <p>Yes. Schedule once (daily, weekly, monthly) and we’ll send on time—fee reminders, service alerts, devotionals, you name it.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Do I get delivery reports?</div>
            <p>Yes. See basic delivery status and totals. Advanced analytics are available on higher plans.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">How do I pay?</div>
            <p>Mobile Money and Card are supported. We’ll right‑size a plan to your volume so you only pay for what you need.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-6">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        <a href="mailto:larryhubservices@gmail.com?subject=Request%20demo%20-%20Larry%20SMS%20Hub&body=Hi%20Larry%20SMS%20Hub%20team%2C%0D%0A%0D%0AWe%27d%20love%20a%20quick%20demo.%20Here%27s%20who%20we%20are%20and%20what%20we%20need%3A%0D%0A-%20Org%20name%3A%0D%0A-%20Use%20case%20(promos%2Ffees%2Falerts)%3A%0D%0A-%20Estimated%20monthly%20SMS%3A%0D%0A%0D%0AThanks!" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white/80">Request demo</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-zinc-300 bg-white/70 text-sm font-semibold hover:bg-white">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
